ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition1
ScalarVariable.description: IntersectionSensor.Sensor1_Active and not pre(IntersectionSensor.Sensor1_Active)

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition10
ScalarVariable.description: train.speed >= train.maxSpeed * train.onUpHillSpeedScale and train.ActiveUpHill

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition11
ScalarVariable.description: train.speed <= train.maxSpeed * train.onUpHillSpeedScale and train.ActiveUpHill

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition12
ScalarVariable.description: train.ActiveUpHill <> pre(train.ActiveUpHill) and not train.ActiveUpHill

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition13
ScalarVariable.description: train.inStation and train.speed > 0.0 and train.lapDistance + train.BreakingDistance + 5.0 >= StationSensor.Sensor1Position - 10.0 and train.lapDistance + train.BreakingDistance - 5.0 <= StationSensor.Sensor1Position - 10.0 and train.state == TrainSimulation.StationSignal.red

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition14
ScalarVariable.description: train.inStation and train.speed <= 0.0 and train.lapDistance + train.BreakingDistance + 5.0 >= StationSensor.Sensor1Position - 10.0 and train.lapDistance + train.BreakingDistance - 5.0 <= StationSensor.Sensor1Position - 10.0 and train.state == TrainSimulation.StationSignal.red

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition15
ScalarVariable.description: train.inStation and train.speed < 45.0 and train.lapDistance + train.BreakingDistance + 5.0 >= StationSensor.Sensor1Position - 10.0 and train.lapDistance + train.BreakingDistance - 5.0 <= StationSensor.Sensor1Position - 10.0 and train.state == TrainSimulation.StationSignal.green

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition16
ScalarVariable.description: train.inStation and train.speed > 0.0 and train.lapDistance + train.BreakingDistance + 10.0 >= StationSensor.Intersection and train.lapDistance + train.BreakingDistance - 10.0 <= StationSensor.Intersection and not train.Arrived

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition17
ScalarVariable.description: train.inStation and train.speed <= 0.0 and train.Arrived

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition18
ScalarVariable.description: train.speed >= 45.0

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition19
ScalarVariable.description: train2.lapDistance >= train2.lap

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition2
ScalarVariable.description: IntersectionSensor.Sensor2_Active <> pre(IntersectionSensor.Sensor2_Active) and not IntersectionSensor.Sensor2_Active and pre(IntersectionSensor.Sensor2_Active)

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition20
ScalarVariable.description: train2.speed >= train2.onCurveSpeed and train2.ActiveCurve

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition21
ScalarVariable.description: train2.speed <= train2.onCurveSpeed and train2.ActiveCurve

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition22
ScalarVariable.description: train2.speed <= train2.maxSpeed and not train2.ActiveCurve and not train2.ActiveUpHill and not train2.inStation

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition23
ScalarVariable.description: train2.speed >= train2.maxSpeed and not train2.inStation

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition24
ScalarVariable.description: train2.speed >= train2.maxSpeed * train2.onUpHillSpeedScale and train2.ActiveUpHill

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition25
ScalarVariable.description: train2.speed <= train2.maxSpeed * train2.onUpHillSpeedScale and train2.ActiveUpHill

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition26
ScalarVariable.description: train2.ActiveUpHill <> pre(train2.ActiveUpHill) and not train2.ActiveUpHill

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition27
ScalarVariable.description: train2.inStation and train2.speed > 0.0 and train2.lapDistance + train2.BreakingDistance + 5.0 >= StationSensor.Sensor1Position - 10.0 and train2.lapDistance + train2.BreakingDistance - 5.0 <= StationSensor.Sensor1Position - 10.0 and train2.state == TrainSimulation.StationSignal.red

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition28
ScalarVariable.description: train2.inStation and train2.speed <= 0.0 and train2.lapDistance + train2.BreakingDistance + 5.0 >= StationSensor.Sensor1Position - 10.0 and train2.lapDistance + train2.BreakingDistance - 5.0 <= StationSensor.Sensor1Position - 10.0 and train2.state == TrainSimulation.StationSignal.red

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition29
ScalarVariable.description: train2.inStation and train2.speed < 45.0 and train2.lapDistance + train2.BreakingDistance + 5.0 >= StationSensor.Sensor1Position - 10.0 and train2.lapDistance + train2.BreakingDistance - 5.0 <= StationSensor.Sensor1Position - 10.0 and train2.state == TrainSimulation.StationSignal.green

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition3
ScalarVariable.description: StationSensor.Sensor1_Active and not pre(StationSensor.Sensor1_Active)

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition30
ScalarVariable.description: train2.inStation and train2.speed > 0.0 and train2.lapDistance + train2.BreakingDistance + 10.0 >= StationSensor.Intersection and train2.lapDistance + train2.BreakingDistance - 10.0 <= StationSensor.Intersection and not train2.Arrived

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition31
ScalarVariable.description: train2.inStation and train2.speed <= 0.0 and train2.Arrived

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition32
ScalarVariable.description: train2.speed >= 45.0

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition33
ScalarVariable.description: Car1.speed >= Car1.maxSpeed

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition34
ScalarVariable.description: Car1.distance + Car1.BreakingDistance + 5.0 >= trainLight.Intersection and Car1.distance + Car1.BreakingDistance - 5.0 <= trainLight.Intersection and Car1.speed > 0.0 and Car1.state == TrainSimulation.TrainLightColor.red

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition35
ScalarVariable.description: Car1.distance < trainLight.Intersection and Car1.state == TrainSimulation.TrainLightColor.on and trainLight.Gate_Angle >= 90.0 and Car1.speed < Car1.maxSpeed

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition36
ScalarVariable.description: Car1.speed <= 0.0

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition37
ScalarVariable.description: Car1.isClumsy >= 1.0 and Car1.distance - Car1.length <= trainLight.Intersection and Car1.distance >= trainLight.Intersection and Car1.speed > 0.0

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition38
ScalarVariable.description: Car2.speed >= Car2.maxSpeed

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition39
ScalarVariable.description: Car2.distance + Car2.BreakingDistance + 5.0 >= trainLight.Intersection and Car2.distance + Car2.BreakingDistance - 5.0 <= trainLight.Intersection and Car2.speed > 0.0 and Car2.state == TrainSimulation.TrainLightColor.red

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition4
ScalarVariable.description: StationSensor.Sensor2_Active <> pre(StationSensor.Sensor2_Active) and not StationSensor.Sensor2_Active and pre(StationSensor.Sensor2_Active)

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition40
ScalarVariable.description: Car2.distance < trainLight.Intersection and Car2.state == TrainSimulation.TrainLightColor.on and trainLight.Gate_Angle >= 90.0 and Car2.speed < Car2.maxSpeed

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition41
ScalarVariable.description: Car2.speed <= 0.0

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition42
ScalarVariable.description: Car2.isClumsy >= 1.0 and Car2.distance - Car2.length <= trainLight.Intersection and Car2.distance >= trainLight.Intersection and Car2.speed > 0.0

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition44
ScalarVariable.description: trainLight.Gate_Angle <= 0.0

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition45
ScalarVariable.description: trainLight.On.active or trainLight.Off.active

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition46
ScalarVariable.description: trainLight.Gate_Angle >= 90.0

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition5
ScalarVariable.description: train.lapDistance >= train.lap

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition6
ScalarVariable.description: train.speed >= train.onCurveSpeed and train.ActiveCurve

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition7
ScalarVariable.description: train.speed <= train.onCurveSpeed and train.ActiveCurve

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition8
ScalarVariable.description: train.speed <= train.maxSpeed and not train.ActiveCurve and not train.ActiveUpHill and not train.inStation

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition9
ScalarVariable.description: train.speed >= train.maxSpeed and not train.inStation
